<p class="govuk-body">Use the numberplate display component to help users identify a vehicle.</p>

<img src="/images/components/numberplate.png" style="max-width:400px;" alt="An image showing the numberplate component in use on an app">

<h2 class="govuk-!-margin-top-5" id="when-to-use-this-component">When to use this component</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">Use this component when it is important to display the numberplate of a vehicle to the user.</p>

<h2 id="when-not-to-use-this-component">When not to use this component</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">Do not use this component to show anything other than a numberplate of a vehicle.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">Do not modify the styling of this component. It is consistent with the style of a UK numberplate.</p>

<h2 id="how-it-works">How it works</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">The component displays letters and numbers in the style of a UK numberplate.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">This is to aid the user in understanding the numberplate of the vehicle they are looking at alongside relevant information.</p>

